data.description: Welcome to the perfect homeownership or investment opportunity! Stunning property offers you the chance to downsize or indulge in an incredible investment venture, whether it's as a rental property or a profitable flip project.      Situated in a prime location, this home grants you easy access to the mall, grocery stores, gas stations, and an array of delightful restaurants.  The absence of HOA fees only adds to the allure of this fantastic property.    But wait there's more!  The ample space provided allows you to effortlessly park your beloved RV, making this residence ideal for adventurous souls.  We invite you to step inside and witness the true beauty of this remarkable abode.  With a price tag well under 300k, and available for USDA financing, it presents an opportunity you simply can't resist.  Don't miss out out on the chance to shape this house into your very own dream home.
